    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"667408\">@Srid</span> it will use its own config file <a href=\"https://github.com/editorconfig-checker/editorconfig-checker/blob/dd3d0a712aa4171c404b80f235cfcafbec5ff20b/README.md?plain=1#L147\">.ecrc</a> instead of following the rules in .editorconfig</p>",
